      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i was looking at my student loan statement and it's kinda frustrating. i've been paying the same amount every month for like a year but the actual amount i owe doesnt seem to be going down as much as i expected. why does it feel like the interest is eating up my payments? can u explain how the math actually works with the principal?",
